 href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijstr.org%2Ffinal-print%2Fnov2015%2FComparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI%26usg%3DAOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34118a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C</a></blockquote><br />\n而家個case係tensile 定shear呀</blockquote><br />\n啱呀，死支那仔淨係識9up<br />\norganic 嘅嘢好多都係 anisotropic <br />\n而且仲有好多因素要考慮<br />\n淨係諗tensile strength 我用玻璃仲勁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留名等睇你哋係香港點用竹取代reinforcing steel bar。 香港建築業未來靠你哋。<br />\n啲竹個面咁滑，點同concrete 有composite action？Bamboo Shear strength 就得嗰30N/mm2 左右。上網搵下資料好難？ 駛唔駛我做個report交埋俾你哋參考每個property？"},{"pid":"a56f2372a1facddbe361f1dd090e9207fed4c213","tid":497573,"uid":95847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母，一班港喱！ 竹硬過鋼，都唔撚知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲係度尻貼新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉！<br />\n如果唔係香港點解搭竹棚唔搭通架！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咗論文先出聲啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijstr.org%2Ffinal-print%2Fnov2015%2FComparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI%26usg%3DAOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34118a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C</a></blockquote><br />\n而家個case係tensile 定shear呀</blockquote><br />\n啱呀，死支那仔淨係識9up<br />\norganic 嘅嘢好多都係 anisotropic <br />\n而且仲有好多因素要考慮<br />\n淨係諗tensile strength 我用玻璃仲勁啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留名等睇你哋係香港點用竹取代reinforcing steel bar。 香港建築業未來靠你哋。<br />\n啲竹個面咁滑，點同concrete 有composite action？Bamboo Shear strength 就得嗰30N/mm2 左右。上網搵下資料好難？ 駛唔駛我做個report交埋俾你哋參考每個property？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.299.5791&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fciteseerx.ist.psu.edu%2Fviewdoc%2Fdownload%3Fdoi%3D10.1.1.299.5791%26rep%3Drep1%26type%3Dpdf&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=05ea0b8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.299.5791&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf</a><br />\n嘢唔識唔緊要，唔好衝出嚟柒。<br />\n<br />\n玻璃唔係無人做，ACI一直都有人研究steel fiber, glass fiber 同 steel bar一齊用，但未係取代囉。"},{"pid":"7ae115ee48e86fda8cb75683bd4971de278ef32d","tid":497573,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d新聞好似作出黎咁"},{"pid":"3a3004a2b9a3c68ba1779d9fddbb61ce62060c97","tid":497573,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母，一班港喱！ 竹硬過鋼，都唔撚知！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲係度尻貼新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉！<br />\n如果唔係香港點解搭竹棚唔搭通架！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇咗論文先出聲啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijstr.org%2Ffinal-print%2Fnov2015%2FComparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Member-In-Building-Construction.pdf%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiZsLbW-IXYAhVBT7wKHYpKDXgQFgg5MAI%26usg%3DAOvVaw3R7tYe5S89S0GAaL-027-C&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34118a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=http://www.ijstr.org/final-print/nov2015/Comparative-Analysis-Of-The-Tensile-Strength-Of-Bamboo-And-Reinforcement-Steel-Bars-As-Structural-Mem